(5)Faculty of Medicine, College of Medicine, Kaohsiung Medical University, 
Kaohsiung, Taiwan; Division of Hepatobiliary, Department of Internal Medicine, 
Kaohsiung Medical University Hospital, Kaohsiung Medical University, Kaohsiung, 
Taiwan.
(6)Institute of Population Health Sciences, National Health Research Institutes, 
Miaoli, Taiwan.
(7)Department of Public Health, College of Health Science, Kaohsiung Medical 
