A variation on chloroplast development: the bizonoplast and photosynthetic 
efficiency in the deep-shade plant Selaginella erythropus.

Sheue CR(1), Liu JW(1), Ho JF(1), Yao AW(2), Wu YH(3), Das S(4), Tsai CC(5), Chu 
HA(6), Ku MS(7), Chesson P(8).

Author information:
